text: You Su-mi is a South Korean taekwondo practitioner. She won a gold medal in flyweight at the 1993 World Taekwondo Championships in New York City, after defeating Águeda Pérez López in the final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:South Korean female taekwondo practitioners Category:World Taekwondo Championships medalists
